quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  26,176,Nawonso anthu okhala m’nkhalango adakana Atumwi
  26,177,"Pamene Shaibu adawauza kuti, “Kodi inu simungaope Mulungu?”"
  26,178,“Ndithudi ine ndine Mtumwi wanu wokhulupirira.”
  26,179,“Opani Mulungu ndipo mundimvere ine.”
  26,180,“Ine sindikupemphani malipiro chifukwa palibe wina aliyense amene angandilipire kupatula Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse.”
  26,181,“Perekani muyeso oyenera ndipo musachepetse.”
  26,182,“Yesani ndi miyeso yabwino.”
  26,183,“Ndipo musawachepetsere anthu zinthu zawo kapena kulowetsa chisokonezo m’dziko.”
  26,184,“Muopeni Iye amene adakulengani inu ndi mibadwo yakale.”
  26,185,"Iwo adati, “Ndithudi iwe walodzedwa.”"
  26,186,“Iwe ndiwe munthu wolingana ndi ife. Ndithudi ife tili kuganiza kuti iwe uli kunama.”
  26,187,“Tigwetsere mtambo kuchokera kumwamba ngati zimene uli kunena ndi zoonadi.”
  26,188,"Iye adati, “Ambuye wanga amadziwa kwambiri chimene inu mumachita.”"
  26,189,Iwo adamukana iye kotero chilango cha thambo ndi moto chidawaononga. Ichi chidali chilango cha tsiku loopsa
  26,190,Ndithudi mu chimenechi muli chiphunzitso koma ambiri a iwo sakhulupirira
  26,191,Ndithudi Ambuye wako ndiye Mwini mphamvu zonse ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha